1865
01:55:21,340 --> 01:55:22,159
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro.

1866
01:55:22,159 --> 01:55:26,619
[SPEAKER_01] Volim kad imam, to znam, kad s prijateljima sjednem,

1867
01:55:26,619 --> 01:55:29,319
